{"title":"css基础","date":"2020-10-02T07:15:23.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年10月2日","L":"2020/10/02","MM-DD":"10-02"},"link":"posts/dfb45e1c","comments":true,"tags":["HTML5+CSS3"],"categories":["网页设计"],"updated":"2020-10-09T06:40:31.792Z","content":"<h1 id=\"css样式规则\">css样式规则<a href=\"#css样式规则\" title=\"css样式规则\"></a></h1><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">选择器&#123;属性1：属性值1；属性2：属性值2；属性3：属性值3；····&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>每条声明由一个属性和属性值组成，以“<strong>键值对</strong>”的形式出现</p>\n<ul><li><p>CSS样式中的选择器<strong>严格区分大小写</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>多个属性之间必须用英文状态下的<code>;</code>隔开</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>若属性的属性值由多个单词组成且中间包含空格，则必须加<code>&quot;&quot;</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">p &#123;font-family:\"Times New Roman\"&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p>在CSS代码中空格是不被解析的，<code>{}``;</code>前后的空格可有可无</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">h1&#123; color:green; font-size:14px; &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">h1&#123; </span><br><span class=\"line\">  \tcolor:green;\t/* 定义颜色的属性*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">  \tfont-size:14px;\t/*定义字体大小属性*/</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>代码2可读性更高</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>属性值和单位之间不能出现<code>空格</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">h1&#123;font-size:14 px; &#125;\t/* 14和单位px之间有空格，浏览器解析时会出现错误*/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul><h1 id=\"引入css样式表\">引入CSS样式表<a href=\"#引入css样式表\" title=\"引入CSS样式表\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"行内式（内联式）\">行内式（内联式）<a href=\"#行内式（内联式）\" title=\"行内式（内联式）\"></a></h2><p>通过标签的<code>style</code>属性来设置标签样式，<strong>没有做到结构与样式分离</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;标签名 style=\"属性1：属性值1；属性2：属性值2；属性3：属性值3；\"&gt;内容&lt;/标签名&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>style</code>：标签的属性</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">h1</span> <span class=\"attr\">style</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"font-size：20px；color：blue；\"</span>&gt;</span>使用CSS行内式修饰一级标签的字体大小和颜色<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"内嵌式\">内嵌式<a href=\"#内嵌式\" title=\"内嵌式\"></a></h2><p><strong>只对其所在的HTML页面有效</strong></p>\n<p><strong>网站不建议使用这种方法，不能充分发挥CSS代码重用的优势</strong></p>\n<p>写在HTML文档的<code>&lt;head&gt;</code>标签之中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text/css\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t选择器&#123;属性1：属性值1；属性2：属性值2；属性3：属性值3；&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;style type=\"text/css\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.red</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:red;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.green</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">color</span>:green;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-class\">.font22</span>&#123;<span class=\"attribute\">font-size</span>:<span class=\"number\">22px</span>;&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">p</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"attribute\">text-decoration</span>:underline; </span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"attribute\">font-family</span>:<span class=\"string\">\"微软雅黑\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/style&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;style&gt;</code>标签一般位于<code>&lt;title&gt;</code>标签之后，也可以放到HTML文档的任何地方</p>\n<h2 id=\"外链式链入式\">外链式(链入式)<a href=\"#外链式链入式\" title=\"外链式(链入式)\"></a></h2><ul><li>同CSS可以被不同的HTML页面链接使用</li>\n<li>外链式是使用频率最高，最实用的CSS样式表</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">link</span> <span class=\"attr\">href</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"css文件的路径\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text/css\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">rel</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"stylesheet\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;link href=\"style.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" /&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>必须指定<code>&lt;link /&gt;</code>标签的3个属性</p>\n<ul><li><code>href</code>：定义所链接外部样式表文件的URL，可以是相对路径，也可以是绝对路径</li>\n<li><code>type</code>：定义所链接文档的类型，<code>&quot;text/css&quot;</code>表示链接的外部文件为CSS样式表</li>\n<li><code>rel</code>：定义当前文档与被链接文档之间的关系，<code>&quot;stylesheet&quot;</code>表示被链接的文档是一个样式表文件</li>\n</ul><h2 id=\"导入式\">导入式<a href=\"#导入式\" title=\"导入式\"></a></h2><ul><li>与外链式相同，针对外部样式表文件</li>\n<li>两者加载时间和顺序不同</li>\n<li>当一个页面被加载时<ul><li><code>&lt;link /&gt;</code>引用的CSS样式表同时被加载</li>\n<li><code>@import</code>会等到页面全部下载完成后再被加载，当网速慢时，会造成不好的用户体验</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text/css\"</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">@import</span> url(css文件路径); 或 <span class=\"keyword\">@import</span> <span class=\"string\">\"css文件路径\"</span>；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">    <span class=\"comment\">/*在此还可以存放其他css样式*/</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text/css\"</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">@import</span> <span class=\"string\">\"style.css\"</span>;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">style</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text/css\"</span> &gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"css\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">@import</span> url(style.css);</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">style</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"设置文本样式\">设置文本样式<a href=\"#设置文本样式\" title=\"设置文本样式\"></a></h1>","prev":{"title":"css选择器","link":"posts/676848e4"},"next":{"title":"线性表","link":"posts/40f24371"},"plink":"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/dfb45e1c/","toc":[{"id":"css样式规则","title":"css样式规则","index":"1"},{"id":"引入css样式表","title":"引入CSS样式表","index":"2","children":[{"id":"行内式（内联式）","title":"行内式（内联式）","index":"2.1"},{"id":"内嵌式","title":"内嵌式","index":"2.2"},{"id":"外链式链入式","title":"外链式(链入式)","index":"2.3"},{"id":"导入式","title":"导入式","index":"2.4"}]},{"id":"设置文本样式","title":"设置文本样式","index":"3"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"DxSummer","link":"<a href=\"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/dfb45e1c/\" title=\"css基础\">https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/dfb45e1c/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2020年10月2日","updated":"2020年10月9日"}}